name: CFNetServicesError
desc: Error codes that may be returned by CFNetServices functions or passed to CFNetServices callback functions.

items.name: case collision
items.desc: An attempt was made to use a name that is already in use.

items.name: case inProgress
items.desc: A search is already in progress.

items.name: case badArgument
items.desc: A required argument was not provided.

items.name: case cancel
items.desc: The search or service was canceled.

items.name: case invalid
items.desc: Invalid data was passed to a CFNetServices function.

items.name: case timeout
items.desc: Resolution failed because the timeout was reached.

items.name: case missingRequiredConfiguration
items.desc: A required configuration for local network access is missing.
